<1.5.0>
- Added: check/cheque system — write checks from any account to a named recipient (first + last name lookup); funds deduct immediately
- Added: check physical item mode — issuer receives a `bank_check` inventory item; recipient double-clicks at a bank to cash it
- Added: check void — issuers can void pending checks, refunding the account
- Added: configurable mail system — supports `bcc-mailbox`, `syn_mail` (direct DB insert), or any custom script via server event
- Added: Spanish, Italian, French, and German localization
- Changed: grant/revoke account and SDB access by character first + last name instead of character ID
- Changed: banker busy lock now respects `Config.UseBankerBusy` and is automatically released on menu close
- Changed: stale account locks from disconnected players are auto-cleared on next access attempt
- Fixed: `Config.UseBankerBusy = false` now correctly disables the busy check

<1.4.1>
- Added the ability to view locked accounts.
- Added options to lock and unlock accounts.
- Added the ability to delete accounts directly from the interface.

<1.3.1>
- Let defaulted loans be repaid and automatically thaw the borrower's accounts once the balance reaches zero.
- Reset is_defaulted alongside the status so cleared loans look like normal paid loans in the DB.
- Fix GetAccountCount to coerce the SQL result into a number, resolving the "Unable to create account" error on fresh installs.
