- Changed: use concatenation instead of `string.format`
- Changed: moved `getMaiboxApi` to `server/services/admin/`
- Changed: `IsBankAdmin` is now global
- Changed: updated `locale.lua`
- Fixed: back buttons
- Fixed: hide Pay button when loan is paid
- Fixed: various localizations
